Repeat: k2; p4 wrapping yarn twice around needle for each purl stitch; k2

p2; sl 4 wyib dropping extra wraps, then with point of left-hand needle, pass the first 2 stitches over the second 2 stitches; return the stitches on the right-hand needle to the left-hand needle and knit all 4 stitches in the crossed order; p2
